3. Troubleshooting¶

This section describes some common issues that can arise and possible solutions.

3.1. Issue #1¶

<Description> .gitignore not ingoring the right file

<Solution> Removing it from the git cache with ‘git rm –cached <filename>’

3.2. Issue #2¶

<Description> Outdated requirements.txt Causing Problems

<Solution> Manually doing a pip install <dependancy-name> for Each Missing Dependancy

3.3. Issue #3¶

<Description> Comparing Two SQLAlchemy Entities with ‘==’ will always Return False

<Solution> Compare Their Table Fields Instead Since Comparing The Entries will Really Compare Their RAM Locations
